data.description: Located in the Desert Plains At Regency Park, this beautifully maintained home by its original owners has 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms with a spacious kitchen ideal for entertaining.  Step outside in the the newly landscaped backyard with a firepit as the focal point which makes for the perfect spot to gather. Additionally, the owners have recently added solar panels to the home to reduce utility costs and new paint throughout.  The home is also equipped with a TESLA charger.
